<%# app/views/record_mailer/email_purchase.text.erb -%>
<%-
  documents ||= @documents || []

  view_debug(__FILE__)
-%>
Thank you for your recent request. The Library has placed an order for your
item and you will be sent an email when it arrives. Items usually arrive in
about 10 business days.
_______________________________________________________________________
<%- documents.each do |doc| -%>
<%-   title  = doc.export_title -%>
<%-   author = doc.show_heading_author -%>
<%-   [title, author].reject(&:blank?).each do |field| -%>
<%=     h(strip_html(field)) %>
<%-   end -%>
<%=   render 'catalog/email/shared/availability', document: doc -%>
_______________________________________________________________________
<%- end -%>

If you have questions about your order, please
Ask a Librarian (<%= URL::ASK_A_LIBRARIAN %>) or review our
Available to Order (<%= URL::ABOUT_PDA %>) information page.

Thank you!

UVA Library Staff
